PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,8,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,9,Fin a storm drain tunnel in north
OL,10,FBelfast on June 27 2020, six days
OL,11,Fafter he left home on his bike to meet
OL,12,Ftwo friends in the Cavehill area of
OL,13,Fthe city.
OL,15,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,16,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,FOver the course of 20 weeks, 76
OL,8,Fwitnesses have given evidence to the
OL,9,Fjury at inquest at Belfast Coroners
OL,10,FCourt, a number of whom have remarked
OL,11,Fon the highly unorthodox nature of the
OL,12,Fcase.
OL,14,FPSNI Detective Chief Inspector
OL,15,FPhillips became the senior
OL,16,Finvestigating officer (SIO) in
OL,17,Frelation to Noah's case on Wednesday
OL,18,F24 June 2020, when it was transferred
OL,19,Fto the Criminal Investigation
OL,20,FDepartment (CID).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,FAt that point, he had been missing for
OL,8,Fthree days.
OL,10,FCounsel for the Coroner, Peter Coll
OL,11,FKC, put it to Mr Phillips: "The
OL,12,Fsituation as we're in this court room
OL,13,Fnow, six months on, the outcome of the
OL,14,Fpolice investigation is that police
OL,15,Fare not able to provide the answer as
OL,16,Fto why Noah did what we know he did,
OL,17,Fwhy he behaved as he did and why he
OL,18,Fdied as he did."
OL,20,FHe replied: "Yes, unfortunately so."
OL,26,@sD@\OUzD@PO]|D@MOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,FMr Coll then asked if, with the
OL,8,Fbenefit of hindsight, there is
OL,9,F"anything that you feel has been
OL,10,Fmissed by police at the time as you
OL,11,Fwent along that has negatively
OL,12,Fimpacted on your ability to understand
OL,13,Fand present an explanation to the jury
OL,14,Fas to what happened?"
OL,16,FMr Phillips said: "There are broadly
OL,17,Fthings that we have missed and
OL,18,Fmistakes made which has left Fiona in
OL,19,Fa position of not having answers.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@UO]xD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,F"In terms of what that would have told
OL,8,Fus in terms of what happened to Noah `
OL,9,FI don't think so."
OL,11,FReferring to a CCTV camera which
OL,12,Fpolice failed to procure footage from,
OL,13,FMr Phillips said: "I'm sorry, that
OL,14,Fshould have been found.
OL,16,F"Fiona shouldn't be sat here six years
OL,17,Fon wondering was there a camera there
OL,18,Fand what did it show," he said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@RO]uD@SOUxD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,FHe added: "With the benefit of
OL,8,Fhindsight we did everything we could
OL,9,Fto find him and I'm content that the
OL,10,FPSNI did everything we could to find
OL,11,Fhim as quickly as we could."
OL,13,FThe officer went on: "Certainly as
OL,14,Ftime has gone on I regularly think if
OL,15,Fthere was something I could have done
OL,16,Fto manage my relationship with Fiona
OL,17,Fin a different way because it
OL,18,Fdeteriorated so quickly.
OL,20,F"I am truly sorry for any part that I
OL,21,Fplayed in that.
OL,26,@oD@KOUsD@\O]uD@VOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,F"Noah's case is unusual enough as it
OL,8,Fis, nobody should be in this position.
OL,10,F"I think six years on, I don't know
OL,11,Fwhat else we could have done to help
OL,12,Fus understand what happened to him and
OL,13,Fwhy."
OL,15,FMr Phillips also said "one of the
OL,16,Fbiggest mistakes made" was that he
OL,17,F"didn't challenge mum's account
OL,18,Fenough" meaning police "didn't look at
OL,19,F(Noah's) actions in the days and weeks
OL,20,Fprior to his disappearance".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@EO]wD@WOUxD@VO]yD@AOUzD@
OL,26,AGO]zD@XOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,F"I'm not for one moment saying Fiona
OL,8,Fdid anything wrong, I should have been
OL,9,Fmore inquisitive into his home life,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,FMr Coll raised a police log showing
OL,13,Fdiscussion of whether the case should
OL,14,Fhave been classed as "critical", with
OL,15,FMr Phillips saying: "Critical does not
OL,16,Fmean we think we've done something
OL,17,Fwrong but critical means we have to
OL,18,Fput the structure in place for public
OL,19,Freassurance."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@eO]vD@VOUvD@_O]wD@UOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,F"We are trying to identify where Noah
OL,8,Fis while also trying to manage an
OL,9,Funparalleled amount of public
OL,10,Finterest," he said.
OL,12,F"The amount of rumours and conspiracy
OL,13,Fthat was flooding the public that Noah
OL,14,Fhad been kidnapped by various parties,
OL,15,Fthat he had been murdered."
OL,17,FHe said there were rumours of
OL,18,F"retribution attack" and police did
OL,19,Fnot know where these were coming from.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@JO]tD@AOUwD@[O]zD@AOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,F"The critique was coming in from the
OL,8,Fpublic that we were in the wrong area,
OL,9,Fthat we weren't doing enough, why
OL,10,Fhadn't we found him," he said.
OL,12,FBrenda Campbell KC, representing Ms
OL,13,FDonohoe, asked if Mr Phillips agreed
OL,14,F"there is an answer" to what happened
OL,15,Fto Noah.
OL,17,FWhen the officer asked for clarity, Ms
OL,18,FCampbell said "Mr Coll just summarised
OL,19,Fto you that police are unable to
OL,20,Fprovide an answer but there must be an
OL,21,Fanswer", to which Mr Phillips agreed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@UO]vD@AOUvD@TO]zD@OOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
