PN,41612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,F"Yes, whether or not we could have
OL,8,Ffound it but we didn't find the
OL,9,Fanswer, no," he said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,FMs Campbell went on to ask Mr Phillips
OL,8,Fa series of short questions ` does he
OL,9,Fknow where Noah went when he was
OL,10,Fcaptured on CCTV leaving his home in
OL,11,Fthe early hours of 21 June, did anyone
OL,12,Fsee him, did he go into a property,
OL,13,Fwhere did he leave his flipflops, how
OL,14,Fdid he get them back, why was his belt
OL,15,Fhanging loose on his return and to
OL,16,Fwhat extent what was that trip linked
OL,17,Fto his disappearance later that same
OL,18,Fday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781722095
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer admits 'mistakes'
OL,4,Cleft Noah Donohoe's mother without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,FMr Phillips answered "I don't know"
OL,8,Fand to the final question said "no, we
OL,9,Fshould have found those answers".
OL,11,FLater, Ms Campbell put it to the the
OL,12,Fofficer that already by that stage in
OL,13,Fher questioning he had "answered on
OL,14,Fmore than 30 occasions 'I don't know'".
OL,16,F"There are many unanswered questions
OL,17,Fin Noah's investigation", she said to
OL,18,Fwhich Mr Phillips agreed.
OL,26,@oD@VOUoD@cO]pD@`OUqD@`O]uD@XOUvD@fO]xD@
OL,26,AAOUyD@XO]
